<p>AND HERE WE ARE</p>
<p>THIS IS IT</p>
<p>I like the D-Class As Main Character Thing we got going on here. He’s semi-competent, has a blank-ish personality with room to grow, and seems reasonably capable of keeping himself not-dead.</p>
<p>Only real question I have is how the civilian world hasn’t ‘really noticed anything yet’, but then again this all probably happens within the same day.</p>
<p>I’m giggling like a dipshit at that ending. Fucking <em>yes</em>.</p>
